<p> 一直以来有对玩木有兴趣而又还没有动过手的朋友想要一些基本的教程，我刚接触玩木的时候看过一个网友的打磨平安无事牌的教程，解说得很是清晰，今天特意翻出来分享，相信对初友有所帮助。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//3d5d/3d5d061dbdb8c4b684441f7578a27a2b.com/large/18ad000804c55b0b743f"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//3ded/3ded158a36f8c9441045822850f8f532.com/large/18560004732d5e7ea24b"></p> 
<p>材料：一块木纹清晰的木料（这里是一块大红酸枝木料）<br></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//6c16/6c163aec54b6f3ad259c37592698c63f.com/large/18ab0007fef3f7610be4"></p> 
<p>打磨工具：60#、150#、320#、800#、1200#砂纸、粗纹打磨棒、金刚锉、抛光块（细）、抛光块（粗）。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//93f8/93f84cc022b2aef66a693da452e631f4.com/large/18b00005e078c2ce48b5"></p> 
<p>辅助工具：直角尺、玻璃板、划线器、针管笔、口罩、手套。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//dc52/dc52c6427d6bfa8f69922c74a004d2e0.com/large/18ac0005dd58fb29afd7"></p> 
<p>一、切割出坯料。</p> 
<p>先在选号的木料上画出坯料的轮廓线，再用切割锯或钢锯按轮廓线切割出规整的牌子坯料。<br></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//f435/f43556095636a5b7ad371ae3e378cd41.com/large/18ac0005e07260825966"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//97fe/97fecc8b4e02625d20630cea6a5e3bc0.com/large/1856000479e9966e0f0d"></p> 
<p>二、粗磨坯料。</p> 
<p>把60#砂纸放在玻璃板上，木牌坯料在砂纸上打磨。打磨时用划8字和垂直上下的方式交换打磨掉两个大面上的锯痕和瑕疵，过程中注意观察平面和转动牌子方向，避免出现某一边打磨过多，牌子坯料变得厚薄不均。打磨牌子四边时用直角尺、针管笔检查所有直边，标记处不规整的多余部分，按顺序打磨平。粗磨是非常关键的部分，打磨时一定要不断观察，有问题及时修正，不要磨过所做的标记线。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//716b/716b3cd6285977b5fd3a87687cdb7546.com/large/18ac0005eddd338eb592"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//0233/02339633f19291bd1eed5c93268ce80d.com/large/1855000035ed8a77ca9d"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//f02c/f02c9e17c2483c8076d971e3bf701379.com/large/18af00000897e54e62b2"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//1543/15435a9305ff2ad7e75eabee29d6151c.com/large/18560004869939f1a6d9"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//cd7c/cd7c2297ea64b5c12e4794718b62f06f.com/large/18b200000301d04d1f53"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//3a14/3a14c1c44790268fe946eaefca0a9f1c.com/large/18af0000089907c301f8"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//2058/205811a272dd1ebafe7bddd37178c699.com/large/18b20000030311f6f3dc"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//784d/784dc3a592e939e18c63e3266f8fbd16.com/large/1855000035ef8edf6b21"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//fbbe/fbbef05ac8214824ec4e23411a60a55d.com/large/18b00005f0e916f0e38c"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//7278/7278b7f609955adf10db321e65572886.com/large/18a90002ef5e56056dd4"></p> 
<p>三、木牌倒直角.<br></p> 
<p>利用划线器、针管笔画出要倒角的边线。画线时握持工具保持固定角度，按照长边、短边、立边和圆角边的顺序，依次使用砂纸、粗纹打磨棒、金刚锉、抛光块（粗）进行倒角。倒角粗磨时打磨的工具斜向运动，磨光时打磨工具要垂直运动。打磨时也要不断观察，这里有个小窍门，把光线调整到人的正对面，这样可以清晰的看到倒角产生的阴影是否笔直。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//036d/036d7261598ef23b2b7f151438adae82.com/large/18af00000edf1d958d79"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//c252/c252e3148bba0bcb2faa4d2a0ae92379.com/large/185600048d602fcad497"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//faaf/faaf35188160bdad805318e76b237b4f.com/large/18af00000ee0bb9a90db"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//8d63/8d63e2ac1c5456a8063535456e52884d.com/large/185500003cfcd52a5c75"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//ad6e/ad6eff9188b80564e1145dee2b4a68e8.com/large/18af00000ee17b0e94b0"></p> 
<p>四、木牌倒圆角。</p> 
<p>先用粗纹打磨棒按小于30度的角磨出一个略小于圆角半径的平面，接着把牌子旋转90度，按照相同的角度打磨到平面一半的位置，再用粗纹打磨棒按45度角磨出第三个平面，最后用金刚锉、抛光块（粗）将三个平面磨圆。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//f0aa/f0aaf0ce1b24cfe29ef6ab5e5aa5ecb0.com/large/1855000043b085fac669"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//1786/1786e83f3b136b87f687f2a074d31da3.com/large/1855000043b146247771"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//72cb/72cbd7c64502d7d59d34fa397a312462.com/large/18af0000155a548f20a9"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//2d0f/2d0fef987e13fb7a0f9ffcb3f6b8d3d1.com/large/18b00005fe73bb7aadea"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//f502/f5029219a01e9bcb995a834cfcbf02a6.com/large/1855000043b480874287"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//62d1/62d1b007b053ae6b83a038061f39142e.com/large/1856000493f419b6ee76"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//8b65/8b654b52ae4164eba060a932be73fcea.com/large/18a90002fcf349e2c5b6"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//6590/659037b3aba2c73171fd473dfa0778ed.com/large/18b00005fe756dd612bf"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//34c9/34c995af2fe4c6d777cf50f9a4412d98.com/large/18a90002fcf45a3fdf0d"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//457e/457eced6b481541486ed1f77bbbe9ae3.com/large/18af0000155fb1258e53"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//01ea/01ea80c2f4bace64a6166a680047d0a3.com/large/18b00005fe77c593561a"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//f2cd/f2cdc0eb4b0053c5aaaab8086cf3ff4a.com/large/18af000015612d190df2"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//4129/4129bdc52f761692da64ca6a02bd187d.com/large/18b200001060c159012a"></p> 
<p>五、精磨木牌。<br></p> 
<p>先使用150#、320#砂纸顺着木纹方向磨去上一目砂纸的痕迹。再用清水洗掉表面的木屑，水洗可以使得表面小木茬立起来，便于下一步的研磨。擦干牌子，迎着光查看表面无划痕、凹陷、瑕疵后，再按800#、1200#砂纸、抛光块（粗）、抛光块（细）顺序抛光。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//7c4f/7c4f7de11d46e94e33f8de773e3ca836.com/large/18af00001b22fda551dd"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//db32/db32640ae94bdcb3dce3c6fd8ab1f5dc.com/large/18ac000600aecbb5d1cd"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//90c7/90c714512f187d674dd33bc96e2a8422.com/large/18ac000600af6b6f883b"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//316b/316bdc79e4664d0669680f20d7a27f1c.com/large/18ac000600b0bc39a872"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//359b/359b44446f5f24a3faf90010e06b80c8.com/large/185500004955b548c7f9"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//5247/5247ad77aad9ade6b6a7c7d5a94d8193.com/large/18ac000600b1ed78f8ce"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//fe42/fe4217a7699b6c98ee7169e597f5bbfd.com/large/18b00006043dc203d56c"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//0e36/0e367e4298251fb3a89234e2662b0f2e.com/large/185500004956cda07b1c"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//e346/e346ce95a7578439e3692c9558799e78.com/large/18af00001b38fffc81d5"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//5745/57451abf8babbbffe0a0ee5dc307e92f.com/large/1856000499dc39691b03"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//9c5c/9c5c7ab1cfd652de58f78e79b0b50043.com/large/18af00001b3a0b20c019"></p> 
<p>六、木牌打孔。<br></p> 
<p>用台钻或手钻两面打2.5mm的小孔（手钻打孔注意保持垂直），再用倒角钻倒角，最后用蜡线打磨内孔。</p> 
